tz_APIGW --> tz_Auth : webhook verify
tz_Auth --> tz_BillingSvc : forward if valid
tz_UserSvc --> tz_Vault
tz_OrderSvc --> tz_Vault
tz_BillingSvc --> tz_Vault
tz_UserSvc --> tz_DB
tz_OrderSvc --> tz_DB
tz_BillingSvc --> tz_DB
tz_APIGW --> tz_CW
tz_UserSvc --> tz_CW
tz_OrderSvc --> tz_CW
tz_BillingSvc --> tz_CW

